# OrangeHRM E2E Tests

When the user asks to run E2E tests or OrangeHRM scenarios:

1. **Default:** run Java POM tests — `mvn test -Dtest=<ModuleTest>` or `mvn clean test` for full suite
2. Load skill: `.cursor/skills/run-orangehrm-e2e/SKILL.md`
3. Tests live in `src/test/java/com/orangehrm/tests/` (14 classes, 72 `@Test` methods)
4. Page objects: `src/main/java/com/orangehrm/pages/`
5. For MCP runs, mirror the Java test flow using `user-selenium` tools

Do not reference CSV runner or `E2eCsvTest` — removed in favor of POM.
